ith technical and computer requirements while attending VMI  Microsoft Software Provided by IT  New computers purchased from the VMI Dell premiere page are preloaded with VMI licensed Microsoft Operating System and Office Software  You must read and agree to the Microsoft Campus Agreement before placing an order with Dell  What computer does VMI recommend  VMI recommends a DELL laptop with 4 year Onsite warranty  With this onsite coverage  the laptops can be worked on here at VMI by a Dell technician instead of the laptop being sent to a repair facility  Cadet owned computers must be a laptop  or notebook computer  No desktop computers will be permitted in barracks All computer systems operating on the VMI LAN must contain a Network Interface Card  NIC  See Computer Recommendations  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 